hoc2015_reinfFeedbackMsg: Ka taea te pēhi te pātene "{backButton}" ki te hoki ki te kēmu.
hoc2015_move_right_instructions: "Me tiki te konganuku para rā [scrapmetal1]. Māhau e tiki, BB-8?"
hoc2015_move_right_down_instructions: "Me tiki he konganuku para anō [scrapmetal2]. Tikina atu ngā konganuku para katoa i tēnei wāhi!"
hoc2015_move_finale_instructions: "Kia 4 ngā maramara konganuku [scrapmetal2]. Māhau e kimi?"
hoc2015_event_two_items_instructions: "R2-D2, he karere arohaehae tāku, māhau e tuku ki ngā Rebel Pilots [rebelpilot]."
hoc2015_event_two_items_instructions2: Nekehia R2-D2 mā ngā pātuhi pehu.
hoc2015_event_four_items_instructions: "Me wawe tōu taenga atu ki ngā Rebel Pilots [rebelpilot] katoa."
hoc2015_score_instructions2: Me tāpiri māka. Ka tāpiritia i te taenga atu o R2-D2 ki ia Rebel Pilot [rebelpilot]. Kia eke ki te 900 ngā māka ki te wini.
hoc2015_win_lose_instructions2: Tāpirihia 100 ngā māka i te whiwhinga o R2-D2 o tētahi Rebel Pilot [rebelpilot]. Tangohia 100 i tōna pānga ki te Stormtrooper [stormtrooper]. Whiwhi 200 ngā māka mō te otinga o te panga. (Whakamahia te Mynock [mynock] kia māmā te mahi.)
hoc2015_add_characters_instructions: "Kua kite au i ngā tohu o ngā mahinga i tēnei aorangi."
hoc2015_add_characters_instructions2: Tāpirihia kia toru ngā Poaka Puffer [pufferpig] ki te aorangi. Kātahi, haere ki te tiki.
hoc2015_chain_characters_instructions2: Ka whiwhi koe i te Tauntaun [tauntaun], kātahi ka puta e rua (nui atu rānei) ngā Mynock [mynock]. Tikinga kia 8 ngā Mynock.
hoc2015_multiply_characters_instructions: Ka taea e koe, te whakaputa i ngā Mouse Droid [mousedroid] e rua, nui atu rānei ia wā ka whiwhi a R2-D2 i tētahi Mouse Droid? Tikina atu kia 20 ngā Mouse Droid.
hoc2015_change_setting_instructions: "Kua tae te wā mō te toro atu ki tētahi aorangi kē."
hoc2015_change_setting_instructions2: Whakamahia ngā tono hou ki te huri te āhua me te tere o tō droid. Kātahi, tikina ngā Rebel Pilots [rebelpilot].
hoc2015_event_free_instructions2: Kei a koe ināanei ngā pukenga katoa hei hanga tō ake kēmu. Kei te pai kia tākaro koe i ngā Tono me ngā Takahanga. Ina, ka mutu koe, pāwhirihia te pātene "Ka Mutu".
